<plot>Phil and Shaun are two struggling filmmakers without a clue but with a celluloid war to wage. In thrall of their own genius, their agendas begin to collide, and the situation is further complicated by tightly-jeaned lothario, Franco, and personal tutor-cum-guru Lucas - who is of absolutely no help whatsoever. As their project spirals out of control, the film unravels into farce in a meta-fictional comedy about greed, responsibility and artistic integrity.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?431133</url></doc>
